Sear

Dependancies
------------

Atlas 0.4.5
ftp://ftp.worldforge.org/pub/worldforge/libs/Atlas-C++

Eris 0.9.5
Get latest CVS version

Varconf 0.5.4
ftp://ftp.worldforge.org/pub/worldforge/libs/varconf

WFmath 0.2.8
Get latest CVS version

Skstream2 0.2.4
Get latest CVS version

SDL 1.2.2 
http://www.libsdl.org/

SDL_image 1.2.2
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image

SDL_mixer 1.2.4
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_mixer/

SigC 1.0.3
http://sourceforge.net/projects/libsigc/

Lib3ds 1.0.2 (now Optional)
http://sourceforge.net/projects/lib3ds/

OpenGL 1.3

Cal3D 0.7 (now Optional)
http://sourceforge.net/projects/cal3d/

MEDIA is not in CVS. Please see ftp for media packs, details on website.
ftp://ftp.worldforge.org/pub/worldforge/clients/sear

For Sear 0.4.x, use media-0.4.0.script and textures.cfg with the existing media pack. Place both these files in top level dir of the media pack.


Please visit website for full instructions. 


Terrain Engine code based up ROAM demo by Bryan Turner. (www.fractalscape.org)


Website: http://www.worldforge.org/dev/eng/clients/sear

